{"tid":2172949,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張達明：律政司撤私人檢控難令人信服基於證據 嘆鄭若驊上任後做法「變晒」","createTime":"2020-08-25T03:14:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T05:07:12.000Z","uid":240362,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6bdc94cbe74b40d34cc3a612d3f21c4190e9f763","tid":2172949,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T03:14:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200825/LCS5KCCDMZFSJBLN2KVAFN2KD4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200825%2FLCS5KCCDMZFSJBLN2KVAFN2KD4%2F&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3SbpLdSN32AczdJcE5lfwVwJ8%3D&h=4688e26d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200825%2FLCS5KCCDMZFSJBLN2KVAFN2KD4%2F&h=71217dbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200825/LCS5KCCDMZFSJBLN2KVAFN2KD4/</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會議員許智峯就西灣河交通警開槍案，及的士司機鄭國泉去年於深水埗鏟上行人路撞人案提私人檢控，惟律政司司長鄭若驊運用權力介入指表證不成立，並獲法庭批准撤控。港大法律學院首席講師張達明在商台節目直言，「法庭基本上無得不接受（律政司要求）」，並指過往類似案件是由刑事檢控專員處理，今次未知「決策係咪又係律政司本人」；而且由於外間不會知道相關證據是否足夠，因此律政司決策過程是否公正客觀、無政治考慮相當重要，但律政司今次並無披露曾否諮詢外間法律意見，難以令人信服是基於證據、法理基礎去決定。"},{"pid":"87b9fbdd0fc6f09c4869a456af101f9c8ae0ed71","tid":2172949,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T03:21:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9f31416cf49b3c500c8f10d8c1cd786a450055df","tid":2172949,"uid":148315,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T03:22:11.000Z","msg":"「惡意檢控」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「瑣碎無聊」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「必然失敗」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基本上單單市民告政府/黑警都係咁"},{"pid":"ee55f501b782288a5d5a25cdb0b581388269a46b","tid":2172949,"uid":94241,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T03:27:23.000Z","msg":"以前覺得袁國強已經夠賤夠仆街.....<br />\n真係一山還有一山高..."},{"pid":"89172a68f4825a336df4902f29aa66f3f92b76c1","tid":